Insider Activity


Individual




Margaret Milner Richardson



Ms. Margaret M. Richardson is Independent Director at Legg Mason, Inc. and a Director & Commissioner at Gulf Coast Funds Management LLC. She is on the Board of Directors at Legg Mason, Inc. and Gulf Coast Funds Management LLC.
Ms. Richardson was previously employed as Non-Executive Chairman by Jackson Hewitt Tax Service, Inc., Partner & National Director-IRS Practice by Ernst & Young LLP, Chairman-Advisory Group by Internal Revenue Service, and an Associate by Sutherland Asbill & Brennan LLP. She also served on the board at Eurasia Foundation, Jackson Hewitt, Inc., National Museum of Women in the Arts, and Piedmont Environmental Council.
She received her undergraduate degree from Vassar College and a graduate degree from George Washington University Law School.



