IRS News Releases
IRS News Releases are released by IRS's Public Affairs Office whenever there is information of importance that needs to be released to the public. Many News Releases pertain to tax treatment of items that you will either be deducting, expensing, or including as income on your tax return.
News Releases are organized by the year they were issued by the IRS. A News Release issued several years ago may have importance to something you are researching for your current year tax return.  News Releases issued in tax year 2006 or earlier are NOT indexed by our search engine, but are included here for research purposes.


